keyValuePair.Value: Why did things go so wrong?
Today's result has confirmed that you'll be relegated this season. It must be hard to take. Why has everything gone so wrong for the team?
It's about responding now.
I'm not sure about making excuses. We have to look forward now. We're in this together and I promise we'll do everything in our power to come back up next season.

We'll need to make changes, definitely.
The thing we really lacked was resilience. I'm not sure these players were ever going to be strong-minded enough. We'll have to look at refreshing the squad before next season, definitely.
Why do you think you've missed out?

Let's not dwell on the past.
Look, this season may have ended in disappointment. But the important thing now is to look forward. We're all in this together and we'll be better next time round.

After a long campaign, today's result means you've missed your chance to qualify for next season's UEFA Europa League. Why do you think your team fell short?
We need to make sure we improve.
